rawData.summary: I have to create monthly report, Quarterly report, semi-annual report and annual report. Under this report we have to show company's IS, BS and CF. For this I have to research company's website and find out 10K, 10Q, Quarterly, Supplement, final press release documents to get the income statement, balance sheet and Cash flow data. Then I have to collate, calculate and tally the data. Also have to find out transaction related data and pass journal entries for company. If any discrepancies are getting then have to research other document also and also have to connect with client for getting the solution. Sometimes I have to do some Adjustments/Reconciliation. After that a new picture of IS, BS and CF are getting cretaed in our terminal and also documents are getting created.
